    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.dieselengine.tooltip=Machine Type: §eCombustion Generator, LCE§r\n§4DEPRECATED - Controller will be removed in next major update!\n§4Check NEI for new Controller and conversion recipe\nSupply Diesel Fuels and §f1,000L§7 of Lubricant per hour to run\nSupply §f40L/s§7 of Oxygen to boost output (optional)\nDefault: Produces §e2,048§7 at §8100%§7 fuel efficiency\nBoosted: Produces §e6,144§7 at §b150%§7 fuel efficiency\nYou need to wait for it to reach §b300%§7 to output full power\nEngine Intake Casings must not be obstructed in front (only air blocks)\n§5480 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
