    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.exofoundry.tooltip=Machine Type: §eFluid Solidifier, Foundry§r\n§616§7 Parallels per §fVoltage§7 Tier\n§a150%§7 Speed\n§8100%§7 EU Usage\nWill §lnot§7 perform §doverclocks§7 over the hatch tier without modules\nWill §lnot§7 process §1§nUIV+§7 voltage tier recipes without modules\nHas §63 Tiers§7, depending on Central Chassis Casing\nHas §62/3/4§7 Module Slots, based on machine tier\nEach Module Slot has §67§7 different options\n§6Modules§7 are selected inside the Controller\n§6Module§7 stats are shown in NEI and the Controller\nToggle Render with Screwdriver\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§cGlorious Evolution!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.exofoundry.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §615§7x§655§7x§615§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center, 2nd layer\n§6   462x §r§7Primary Exo-Foundry Casing (minimum)\n§6   548x §r§7Exo-Foundry Containment Glass\n§6   281x §r§7Inner Foundry Siphon Casing\n§6   260x §r§7Central Magnetic Chassis (tiered)\n§6   224x §r§7Netherite Frame Box\n§6   196x §r§7Central Exo-Foundry Regulation Casing\n§6   173x §r§7Black Plutonium Item Pipe Casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Foundry Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Foundry Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Foundry Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Foundry Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6chassis§r§7 for §6Magnetic Chassis Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n   Check NEI for Module structure costs\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
