    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipassemblycomplex.name=Комплекс сборки наночипов
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipassemblycomplex.tooltip=Machine Type: §eNAC, Nanochip-Assembly-Complex§r\nUses Circuit Components (§eCCs§7) to create circuits at unimaginable speeds\nClick the Logo Icon in the GUI for more information\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§eCCs§7 can only exist in the perfect environment present in §fVacuum Conveyor Hatches§7\nConvert items to §eCCs§7 in the control room by placing them in a §cc§eo§al§3o§br§de§5d§7 input bus\nEvery §45§7 seconds, all items in §cc§eo§al§3o§br§de§5d§7 input buses are placed\nin Vacuum Conveyor Outputs (§eVCOs§7) of the same §cc§eo§al§bo§dr§7\nFinished circuit §eCCs§7 are converted back into circuits by routing them to a §eVCI§7 in the control room\n§eCCs§7 in a §cc§eo§al§3o§br§de§5d§7 §eVCI§7 are placed in an output bus of the same §cc§eo§al§bo§dr§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§eCCs§7 must be processed into a refined version by §f§nmodules§r§7 before they\ncan be assembled into a circuit in the §aNanochip Assembly Matrix\nAll power from the energy hatch is distributed to the modules as they need it\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§d§oHome of the Gestalt Rapidly Evolving Genesis Optimization System (GREGOS),§7\n§d§oa pseudo-sentient program overseeing circuit production in the NAC§7\n§d§oIt seems to be eager to learn more, maybe you can become friends?§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
