    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.pcbcoolingtower.name=Градирня
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.pcbcoolingtower.tooltip=Machine Type: §ePCB Factory Upgrade§r\nThe Cooling Tower enables overclocking of the PCB Factory\nTier 1 gives a normal overclock\nTier 2 gives a §6perfect§7 overclock\nIt requires 10L/s of cooling fluid per active and connected PCB Factory\nTier 1 Cooling Fluid is: §6Distilled Water\nTier 2 Cooling Fluid is: §6Super Coolant\n§7Place the controller block within §c16§7 blocks of the PCB Factory\n§7Left click the PCB Factory controller with a data stick,\n§7then right click this controller to link.\n§7Can connect to many PCB Factories!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§9§lBlue§b§lWeabo§r§7 & §a§f§lgu§b§lid§3§l118§r§7
